		<title>15EMPLOYMENT OF PARENTS</title>
		<content> Seventy questionnaires were sent home 
 to find out where parents worked.     
                                       
 LOCATION         FATHERS  MOTHERS     
 ________         _______  _______     
 Leicester          50%      17%       
 Coventry           03%      00%       
 Broughton Astley   09%      23%       
 Elsewhere          38%      23%       
                                       
       Unemployed   00%      37%       
                                       
 It is clear that the majority of      
 parents do not work in the village.   
 Therefore Broughton Astley would be   
 classed as a{"Dormitory Village"}.    
 There are only two factories in the   
 village,one prints designs on balloons
 and the other is a hosiery firm.      
                                       
                                       
